# Third-party skills are installer-managed and reproducible — they are NOT
# ours to redistribute (license belongs to their authors). Provenance lives in
# .skill-lock.json (skills CLI) or a per-skill .skillfish.json (skillfish).
# Reinstall from those records; never commit the content here.
skills/*

# Own, original skills — explicitly tracked. Add a `!skills/<name>/` line
# when authoring a new skill (and only after a privacy pass — this repo is public).
!skills/browser-screenshot/
!skills/homepage-icon-finder/

# Python bytecode from compile checks
__pycache__/
*.pyc
